### ============================================
### NOTES & FIXES
### ============================================
#
# ✅ FIXES APPLIED:
# 1. ❌ "notes" field removed from CREATE requests
#    → Add notes later via PATCH
#
# 2. ✅ Use actual incident IDs from GET response
#    → Check STEP 2 for real IDs
#
# 3. ✅ Use valid storeId (7) from seeded data
#    → Watsons Siam Paragon (id: 7)
#
# 4. ✅ equipmentId is now OPTIONAL
#    → Only include if you have valid equipment
#
# ============================================
# REQUIRED FIELDS (CreateIncidentDto):
# ============================================
# - title: String (required)
# - description: String (required)
# - storeId: Number (required, must exist)
# - priority: Enum (required: CRITICAL, HIGH, MEDIUM, LOW)
# - category: Enum (optional: HARDWARE, SOFTWARE, NETWORK, SYSTEM, OTHER)
# - equipmentId: Number (optional, must exist if provided)
#
# ❌ NOT ALLOWED in CREATE:
# - notes (add via PATCH later)
# - status (auto-set to PENDING/OPEN)
# - incidentCode (auto-generated)
# - assignedToId (use /assign endpoint)
# - resolvedById (use /resolve endpoint)
#
# ============================================
# WORKFLOW:
# ============================================
# 1. Create → POST /incidents (no notes!)
# 2. Add Notes → PATCH /incidents/:id {notes}
# 3. Assign → POST /incidents/:id/assign
# 4. Update → PATCH /incidents/:id {notes}
# 5. Resolve → POST /incidents/:id/resolve
#
# ============================================
# COMMON ERRORS & SOLUTIONS:
# ============================================
#
# Error: "property notes should not exist"
# Solution: Remove "notes" from CREATE request
#
# Error: "Incident with ID X not found"
# Solution: Use incident CODE (INC-2025-XXXX) or check actual IDs
#
# Error: "storeId must be a valid store"
# Solution: Use storeId 7 (Watsons Siam Paragon)
#
# Error: 500 Internal Server Error
# Solution: Check equipmentId exists or remove it
#
# ============================================
# END OF FIXED INCIDENT API TESTS
# ============================================
